The paper deals with unsupervised document embedding, which is a common problem in natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a convolutional neural network (CNN) architecture, which is a popular deep learning technique used in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses unsupervised learning algorithms (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques. Finally, the paper proposes a method for learning semantic structure within documents, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
